Class StackList

com.ultreon.modlib.silentlib.collection.StackList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<net.minecraft.world.item.ItemStack>, Collection<net.minecraft.world.item.ItemStack>, List<net.minecraft.world.item.ItemStack>, RandomAccess
public final class StackList extends ArrayList<net.minecraft.world.item.ItemStack>
ArrayList designed to hold non-empty ItemStacks. Ignores any empty stacks that are added. Has some convenience methods for selecting stacks.
Since:
3.0.0(?)
